<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.2.4">
<l>kōtil vaṇpukaḻ koṇṭu camayikaḷ</l>
<l>pētaṅkaḷ collip pitaṟṟum pirāṉparaṉ</l>
<l>pātaṅkaṇ mēlaṇi paimpoṟ ṟuḻāyeṉṟē</l>
<l>yōtumā lūḻviṉai yēṉṟaṭat tōḷiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“The fresh golden Tulsi [that is the] decoration on the feet</l>
<l>of the highest, the lord, about whom babble, speaking at variance,</l>
<l>the sectarians with faultless liberal praise”,</l>
<l>thus recites she with broad shoulders of me with deeds that mature.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
